### Commit 602c0271
Message: [DOCS] Verify README is current with latest features

Reviewed README against recent commits (ea9a090, f981564 - DRY refactoring).
All current user-facing features are documented:
- Installation and quick start
- Configuration and permissions
- Claude Code integration (statusline + skills)
